flowchart TD
  A[Leadership problem] --> B[State strongest reason not to add framework]
  B --> C{Problem driver}
  C -- service operations --> D[ITSM / ITIL]
  C -- board governance --> E[COBIT]
  C -- enterprise architecture --> F[TOGAF / ISO 42010]
  C -- legal or audit exposure --> G[PCI / HIPAA / GDPR / PDP / SOC 2]
  C -- project control --> H[PMBOK]
  C -- process variation --> I[Lean Six Sigma]
  C -- cloud-native platform --> J[CNCF plus architecture review]
  C -- vendor market scan --> K[Gartner plus due diligence]
  C -- delivery performance --> L[DORA / MTTR]
  C -- scale coordination --> M[SAFe or lighter portfolio model]
  D --> N[Define owner, scope, evidence, metrics]
  E --> N
  F --> N
  G --> O[Mark legal/version items: This needs verification]
  H --> N
  I --> N
  J --> N
  K --> N
  L --> N
  M --> N
  O --> N
  N --> P{Adoption cost proportional to risk?}
  P -- yes --> Q[Adopt or adapt minimum viable implementation]
  P -- no --> R[Reject, defer, or use smaller artifact]
